OL,4,CUK recovery slows as staff shortages
OL,5,Cplague firms
OL,6, Staff and supply shortages have taken
OL,7, their toll on the UK's economic
OL,8, recovery this month, according to a
OL,9, closely watched survey.
OL,11,FThe IHS Markit/CIPS Composite
OL,12,FPurchasing Managers' Index (PMI) for
OL,13,FAugust hit a six-month low of 55.3,
OL,14,Ffalling from 59.2 in July.
OL,16,FAny reading above 50 indicates growth,
OL,17,Fbut the bounce-back from the pandemic
OL,18,Fis losing momentum, said researchers.
OL,20,FCIPS group director Duncan Brock said
OL,21,Fthe figures were "a stark warning".
